title: Gayming LIVE 2023 Livestream
description:
Get ready for Gayming Live 2023 to kick off on October 6th. IGN will be running limited programing to showcase some of the best games, talent, and professionals from the LGBTQIA+ community. Catch our stream starting at 12:30pm (ET) to find out what happening and don't forget to follow Gayming Live for the rest of the weekend for even more amazing games, interesting creators, and one of the biggest communities around. 

Indie Showcase
We showcase a handpicked selection of the diverse LGBTQ+ indie games that have been submitted for our Indie Festival

Barbie Horse Adventures Speed Run
Giddy up for an electrifying spectacle as drag artist Mynxie aims to break a world record in a high-speed Barbie game run!

Creating Safe Online Communities
Join us for an engaging panel discussion on the vital topic of creating safe and inclusive online communities within the gaming space.

title: Cricket 24 - Official Launch Trailer
description:
Cricket 24 is available now on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, and PC. Cricket 24 for Nintendo Switch will be available in November 2023. Check out the launch trailer to see what to expect from Cricket 24, which features a career mode, official licenses, and more. 

In Cricket 24, you will be able to take on major cricket nations including Australia and England in the official Ashes, West Indies, New Zealand, Ireland and more, plus for the first time ever, professional Indian T20 teams, all set in over 50 detailed official stadiums.

title: Horizon: An American Saga - Two-Part Release Date Announcement Teaser
description:
Kevin Costner stars, directs, and produces the two-part Western epic Horizon: An American Saga. The cast also includes Sienna Miller, Sam Worthington, Jena Malone, Abbey Lee, Michael Rooker, Danny Huston, Luke Wilson, Isabelle Fuhrman, Jeff Fahey, Will Patton, Tatanka Means, Owen Crow Shoe, Ella Hunt, and Jamie Campbell Bower.

Horizon: An American Saga films One and Two will have a dual theatrical release, kicking off June 28, 2024 with the second film debuting August 16, 2024.

title: Loki Season 2 - Official 'Loki's Greatest Hits' Trailer (2023) Tom Hiddleston, Owen Wilson
description:
Take a trip down memory lane with Loki's greatest hits as we lead up to Episode 1 of Marvel Studios’ Loki Season 2. From Thor to Loki Season 2, how will Loki grow beyond his glorious purpose and seek a new calling with the fate of everything that is, ever was, and everything that will be in the palm of his hand?

Loki Season 2 stars Tom Hiddleston (Loki), Owen Wilson (Mobius), Sophia Di Martino (Sylvie), Ke Huy Quan, Gugu Mbatha-Raw (Ravonna Renslayer), Tara Strong (Miss Minutes), Wunmi Mosaku (Hunter B-15) and more. The series was created by Michael Waldron with Kevin R. Wright and Tom Hiddleston as executive producers. 

Loki Season 2 will start streaming tonight on Disney Plus on October 5 at 6 PM PT.

title: Assassin's Creed: Mirage PS5 vs Xbox Series X|S vs PS4 vs Xbox One Performance Review
description:
Assassin's Creed Mirage releases this week on PS5, Xbox Series X|S, PC, PS4, and Xbox One after a 3-year hiatus. AC Mirage is a cross-generation title that offers dual modes on current gen consoles with 4K or 60fps options. Are the last generation consoles showing their age? How much better are the current generation machines? Does the Xbox Series S bridge the gap between them? We eagle dive into another big IGN performance review.

title: The Marvels - Official Teaser Trailer (2023) Brie Larson, Teyonah Parris, Iman Vellani
description:
Check out the latest teaser for The Marvels for another look at this upcoming movie starring Brie Larson, Teyonah Parris, Iman Vellani, Zawe Ashton, Gary Lewis, Seo-Jun Park, Zenobia Shroff, Mohan Kapur, Saagar Shaikh, and Samuel L. Jackson.

In Marvel Studios’ The Marvels, Carol Danvers aka Captain Marvel has reclaimed her identity from the tyrannical Kree and taken revenge on the Supreme Intelligence. But unintended consequences see Carol shouldering the burden of a destabilized universe. When her duties send her to an anomalous wormhole linked to a Kree revolutionary, her powers become entangled with that of Jersey City super-fan Kamala Khan, aka Ms. Marvel, and Carol’s estranged niece, now S.A.B.E.R. astronaut Captain Monica Rambeau. Together, this unlikely trio must team up and learn to work in concert to save the universe as “The Marvels.” 

The Marvels is directed by Nia DaCosta, and Kevin Feige is the producer. Louis D’Esposito, Victoria Alonso, Mary Livanos and Matthew Jenki

Red Dead Redemption Finally Gets a 60FPS Update - IGN Daily Fix
description:
In today's Daily Fix:
Rockstar's latest port of Red Dead Redemption was met with criticism for being locked at 30fps on modern consoles, but a new patch just casually dropped a 60fps update without much fanfare. The catch? It's currently PS5-only, so if you bought the latest version on Switch or Xbox Series, you're still stuck with 30fps for now. PS5 owners are also getting first dibs on the upcoming Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 multiplayer beta, which goes live October 6 until October 8. And we take a look at the current Pringles Icons leaderboard.
Presented by Pringles.

title: Assassin's Creed Mirage: 13 Combat and Stealth Tips
description:
Assassin’s Creed has been many things over the years, and Mirage seeks to evoke the gameplay of the series’ origins while also offering a unique spin. Stealth gameplay has seen a much larger emphasis here, and all-out combat is a bit trickier than in previous games. Whether you’re looking to brandish your sword against every guard you come across or stick to the shadows, here’s 13 Combat and Stealth tips for Assassin’s Creed Mirage.
